'''''The Adjudicator''''', or '''''The Adjudicator Holofeed''''', was a trade publication for [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] during the time of the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. It was edited by [[Krav Noblis]].

==Issues==
*{{KOTORbackups|14}}
*{{KOTORbackups|20}}
*{{KOTORbackups|23}}

==Behind the scenes==
''The Adjudicator'' is one of a number of "news organs" based on the ''[[Taris Holofeed]]'' that were included as extras in monthly issues of [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic (comic series)|''Knights of the Old Republic'']] starting with [[Knights of the Old Republic 13|issue 13]].

